David McLean (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_McLean_(actor) 0 David McLean (born May 19, 1922, Akron, Ohio – d. October 12, 1995, Culver City, California) was an American film and television actor, best known for appearing in many Marlboro television and print advertisements beginning in the early 1960s.
